{"tid":51794,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"懷才不遇的蘇仔","createTime":"2016-12-23T13:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T19:25:45.000Z","uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d656b2baa845606689a637ef720df41633afd6a4","tid":51794,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T13:40:38.000Z","msg":"我叫做蘇仔，今年21歲。畢業咗一年，我見咗唔少工，好似 Goldman Xachs, HXBC咁嘅大公司， 但居然全部無回音。<br />\n<br />\n見咗咁多份工，我覺得香港係一個埋沒人才嘅地方。就好似HXBC 咁，我講明我夢想係做銀行家，但係就連in嘅機會都冇，而且我唔止Gpa有 3.4，去過深圳做交流生，仲要ielts 7 分，點解連in都冇得in？<br />\n<br />\n諗起我小學讀精英班，中學讀 band 1，公開試有 Full cert，最後讀 Business Administration，都可以算叫做社會嘅精英。但原來呢啲精英連 Interview嘅機會都冇。<br />\n<br />\n「喂～呀蘇，你做緊咩工呀？」中學同學張六常問我。<br />\n<br />\n「KFC Manager」<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻我真係好灰機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772a5b77226699c935caa114a9868ecabdafc609","tid":51794,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"主旨：唉&hellip;香港真係好多好似蘇仔咁樣嘅叻人、聰明人懷才不遇，覺得好可惜"},{"pid":"bc56ab5c9df75f66481022ff8ee94fc0286efc1f","tid":51794,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f9543d99c5d3993f88c3c6f0d6a2a7b82a3ae48","tid":51794,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"好似幾好"},{"pid":"3e70069d89780aa63b2d9ea431f9589660247dec","tid":51794,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6020254af7ca80889828199d156e24154fd5fc","tid":51794,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似幾好</blockquote><br />\n藺相如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990eb4b32472994d21b4e4084d01b64ac2c224d8","tid":51794,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"佢以前有冇好想玩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33e639c69b7d7b48476bf13e28f061d4dc613d2","tid":51794,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢以前有冇好想玩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}